title: Martha Bakes (Recipes H-Y)
description:
The Martha Stewart Bakes Series - Recipes H through Y

is based on a lifetime of research and baking techniques perfected by Martha Stewart. 

In these TV programs Martha demonstrates one specific culinary discipline, home bakers will get the tools they need to create the finest desserts and baked goods in their own kitchen.
